Package: framedf
Type: Package
Title: Fast Relationship Triage for Data Frames
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Gilles", "Colling", email = "gilles.colling051@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3070-6066"))
Description: Fast primitives for screening pairwise relationships in data frames.
    Performs numeric association screening, categorical-numeric group comparisons,
    and partial residualization against adjustment sets. Designed for repeated
    tiny regressions and relationship triage, not model fitting.
